data.description: Amazing curb appeal with the first thing you will notice is the unique Turret and entry way when you drive up. High quality craftsmanship and charm w/custom finishes & fixtures throughout. High coffered ceilings, rich warm custom woods used for all doors, cabinets & vanities. Beautiful brand new laminate flooring in living areas w/carpet in 3 of 4 bedrooms (1 bedroom is being used as office). Tile in bathrooms. Large living room with rock surround w/cozy gas fireplace makes it feel like home. Wonderful kitchen w/granite countertops that opens to dining room, eating bar and there are stainless appliances & tons of cabinetry w/under cabinet lighting. Main bedroom includes tile stall shower, granite counter, jetted tub, double vanity & large closet. Slider off dining room opens to a covered patio. Easy care yard with vegetable garden & 3 budding apple trees. There is a narrow access/parking area along one side of house for a small boat or extra vehicle.
